research_municipality_step.notes: Lumberton, Texas operates under a Mayor-Council government. There was a discrepancy in sources regarding the Mayor Pro Tem role; the City of Lumberton's official website lists Kenneth Wahl as Mayor Pro Tem, while other directories list Joey Schoen. The information from the City of Lumberton's website was prioritized for this response. No specific ward or district divisions were found for the council members.
